description:
ASP.NET File Upload like GMail


Ajax Uploader is an easy to use, hi-performance ASP.NET File Upload Control which allows you to upload multiple files to web server without refreshing the page. It's also available for Classis ASP and PHP.

This file upload control uploads large files to a server with low server memory consumption. Also compatible with legacy browsers.

For ASP.NET Core Blazor applications, please use Blazor uploader.

Deployment:
http://ajaxuploader.com/Deployment.htm

Demo:
http://ajaxuploader.com/demo/

Download:
http://ajaxuploader.com/download/Ajax-Uploader.zip
